  "name": "WF8b - Social Post Platform Publishing",
  "active": true,
  "note": "Exported from live n8n (knurdz3o.app.n8n.cloud) on 2026-07-17. Live workflow id: VZ9ZaA1S2JxSAeGQ. REQUIRED: on any failure path, POST to /api/internal/n8n/post-result with { postId, status: 'failed', error } so posts do not stay stuck in publishing.",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## WF8b — post-result writeback (REQUIRED on failure)\n\nSuccess path today PATCHes `social_posts` directly (`Mark Post Published`). **Any error branch must also call** `POST {NEXUS_APP_URL}/api/internal/n8n/post-result` with Bearer `N8N_INGEST_TOKEN` and body `{ postId, status: 'failed', error }` so the post leaves `publishing` instead of hanging.\n\nOn full success, prefer the same endpoint with `{ postId, status: 'published' }` (service-role writeback) instead of a direct Supabase PATCH — the browser cannot write terminal statuses.",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 440
      },
      "id": "b8b00001-0000-4000-8000-000000000001",
      "name": "Sticky Note — post-result",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -200,
        180
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ad76d65c-3ade-4a86-aa39-d018e49f653d",
      "name": "Publish Request",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [
        240,
        300
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "path": "publish-social-post",
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "responseMode": "responseNode"
      },
      "webhookId": "c08a827b-4f9e-4f37-8d27-ebde7c7723f1"
    },
    {
      "id": "f82164ac-017b-4c92-be2f-79af14897d64",
